            <li>1 hour minimum charge</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="tel:07399676656" class="btn btn-navy btn-full">Call Now</a>
        </div>

        <div class="pf-price-card">
          <div class="pf-price-tier">WEEKEND EMERGENCY</div>
          <div class="pf-price-name">Saturday to Sunday</div>
          <div class="pf-price-sub">9am to 1pm</div>
          <div class="pf-price-amount">£120<small>/hr</small></div>
          <ul class="pf-price-list">
            <li>Same fast service</li>
            <li>Gas Safe engineer</li>
            <li>Parts at cost only</li>
            <li>1 hour minimum charge</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="tel:07399676656" class="btn btn-navy btn-full">Call Now</a>
        </div>

        <div class="pf-price-card pf-price-card-featured">
          <div class="pf-price-badge">MOST COMMON</div>
          <div class="pf-price-tier">OUT OF HOURS</div>
          <div class="pf-price-name">Nights and Holidays</div>
          <div class="pf-price-sub">Anytime, 24/7</div>
          <div class="pf-price-amount">£150<small>/hr</small></div>
          <ul class="pf-price-list">
            <li>24/7 Liverpool cover</li>
            <li>Emergency priority response</li>
            <li>Gas Safe engineer</li>
            <li>1 hour minimum charge</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="tel:07399676656" class="btn btn-orange btn-full" style="color:#ffffff;">Call Now. We Answer.</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="pf-info-bar" style="margin-top:2rem;">
        <p style="font-size:0.9rem;color:var(--text);font-weight:600;">1 hour minimum on all call-outs. After the first hour we charge in 30 minute increments. Parts at cost. Written quote before any work begins. Most emergency jobs take 30 to 90 minutes.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="pf-alert" style="margin-top:1.25rem;">
        <strong>What most Liverpool emergency plumbing jobs actually cost</strong>
        <p>Burst pipe: £120 to £350 · Boiler breakdown: £150 to £500 · Blocked drain: £80 to £250 · Gas leak safety visit: FREE · Major leak: £80 to £200. For independent price benchmarks see <a href="https://www.checkatrade.com/blog/cost-guides/emergency-plumber-cost/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Checkatrade's emergency plumber cost guide</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- COMMON JOBS -->
  <section class="pf-section" style="background:#f1f5f9;">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Common Emergencies We Fix Across Liverpool</h2>
      <p class="pf-sub">The plumbing faults we attend most frequently across Liverpool L1 to L40.</p>
      <div class="jobs-grid" style="margin-top:2rem;">
        <div class="job-card"><h3>Burst Pipe and Water Coming Through Ceiling</h3><div class="job-meta"><span class="job-price">£120 to £350</span><span class="job-time">30 to 90 mins</span></div><p>Water pouring from pipes, ceiling or walls. We stop the leak, repair or replace the pipe section and check for hidden damage. Common in winter in Liverpool's Victorian properties with external pipes.</p></div>
        <div class="job-card"><h3>No Hot Water and Boiler Breakdown</h3><div class="job-meta"><span class="job-price">£150 to £500</span><span class="job-time">45 to 120 mins</span></div><p>No hot water, radiators cold, error codes showing. We diagnose and repair on the same visit. Common issues: pressure, pilot light, pump and PCB failures. Gas Safe engineers only.</p></div>
        <div class="job-card"><h3>Blocked Toilet and Blocked Drain Liverpool</h3><div class="job-meta"><span class="job-price">£80 to £250</span><span class="job-time">30 to 90 mins</span></div><p>Toilet not flushing, sink not draining, shower backing up. We use professional drain equipment to clear blockages. Tree roots in Victorian Liverpool sewers are a very common cause.</p></div>
        <div class="job-card job-card--warning"><h3>Gas Leaks</h3><div class="job-meta"><span class="job-price">FREE safety visit</span><span class="job-time">Priority response</span></div><p>Smell of gas or hissing sound near gas pipes or appliances. We respond immediately. First visit to make safe is FREE. <a href="https://cadentgas.com/gas-escapes" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="font-weight:700;">Call Cadent Gas on 0800 111 999</a> first if you smell gas.</p></div>
        <div class="job-card"><h3>Major Leaks</h3><div class="job-meta"><span class="job-price">£80 to £200</span><span class="job-time">20 to 60 mins</span></div><p>Leaking taps, pipes under the sink, toilet leaks or radiator leaks. We identify the source, stop the leak and repair or replace the faulty component before it causes further damage.</p></div>
        <div class="job-card"><h3>Heating Failure</h3><div class="job-meta"><span class="job-price">£120 to £350</span><span class="job-time">60 to 120 mins</span></div><p>Heating not working, some radiators cold, boiler fires but no heat. We check pump, motorised valves, thermostats and pipework. Priority response in winter for vulnerable occupants.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- OTHER SERVICES -->
  <section class="pf-section" style="background:#f1f5f9;">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 style="text-align:center;">All Plumbing and Heating Services in Liverpool</h2>
      <p class="pf-sub" style="text-align:center;">Not an emergency? We cover the full range of plumbing and heating work across Liverpool and Merseyside.</p>
      <div class="services-grid" style="margin-top:2rem;">
        <a href="/boiler-installation-liverpool" class="service-card" style="background:#ffffff;border:1px solid #e2e8f0;border-left:3px solid var(--orange);display:flex;flex-direction:column;">
          <strong style="color:var(--navy);">Boiler Installation Liverpool</strong>
          <span style="color:var(--text);flex:1;">New combi, system and regular boilers from £1,800. Worcester Bosch, Vaillant, Ideal. 10 year warranty.</span>
          <span style="display:block;margin-top:0.75rem;color:var(--orange);font-weight:700;font-size:0.88rem;">View service &rarr;</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/boiler-service-liverpool" class="service-card" style="background:#ffffff;border:1px solid #e2e8f0;border-left:3px solid var(--orange);display:flex;flex-direction:column;">
          <strong style="color:var(--navy);">Boiler Service Liverpool</strong>
          <span style="color:var(--text);flex:1;">Annual boiler service £120. Gas Safe engineer. Benchmark updated. Certificate same day.</span>
          <span style="display:block;margin-top:0.75rem;color:var(--orange);font-weight:700;font-size:0.88rem;">View service &rarr;</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/gas-safety-certificate-liverpool" class="service-card" style="background:#ffffff;border:1px solid #e2e8f0;border-left:3px solid var(--orange);display:flex;flex-direction:column;">
          <strong style="color:var(--navy);">Gas Safety Certificates Liverpool</strong>
          <span style="color:var(--text);flex:1;">CP12 landlord certificates from £80. Same-day available. Combined with service for £175.</span>
          <span style="display:block;margin-top:0.75rem;color:var(--orange);font-weight:700;font-size:0.88rem;">View service &rarr;</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/power-flushing-liverpool" class="service-card" style="background:#ffffff;border:1px solid #e2e8f0;border-left:3px solid var(--orange);display:flex;flex-direction:column;">
          <strong style="color:var(--navy);">Power Flushing Liverpool</strong>
          <span style="color:var(--text);flex:1;">Cold radiators or noisy boiler? Power flush from £350. Warranty protection included.</span>
          <span style="display:block;margin-top:0.75rem;color:var(--orange);font-weight:700;font-size:0.88rem;">View service &rarr;</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/central-heating-installation-liverpool" class="service-card" style="background:#ffffff;border:1px solid #e2e8f0;border-left:3px solid var(--orange);display:flex;flex-direction:column;">
          <strong style="color:var(--navy);">Central Heating Liverpool</strong>
          <span style="color:var(--text);flex:1;">Full central heating systems from £3,500. Radiator additions from £200. ECO4 grants available.</span>
          <span style="display:block;margin-top:0.75rem;color:var(--orange);font-weight:700;font-size:0.88rem;">View service &rarr;</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/radiators-liverpool" class="service-card" style="background:#ffffff;border:1px solid #e2e8f0;border-left:3px solid var(--orange);display:flex;flex-direction:column;">
          <strong style="color:var(--navy);">Radiators Liverpool</strong>
          <span style="color:var(--text);flex:1;">New radiator supply and fit from £200. TRV upgrades from £50. System balancing included.</span>
